Install Sage Theme

//1st Run
npm install -g gulp bower
//2nd Run 
git clone https://github.com/roots/sage.git theme-name
composer create-project roots/sage NS dev-master
chmod -R 777 newsagetheme
ls -lrt
//3rd run
yarn
//4th

Available build commands
Run these script commands within your theme directory:

yarn run build — Compile and optimize the files in your assets directory
yarn run build:production — Compile assets for production
yarn run start — Compile assets when file changes are made, start Browersync session

yarn run start


//
cd etc/apache2
cd custom-sites
